    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Your letter dated December 6, 1954, has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "been received.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Although I would like to be of service,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "information in FBI files is confidential and avail-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "able for official use only. I would like to point",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "out also that this Bureau is strictly a fact-finding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "agency and does not make evaluations or draw conclu-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "sions as to the character or integrity of any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "individual, publication or organization.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "I know you will understand the reason for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "these rules and will not infer either that we do or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "that we do not have the information you desire.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
