    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "NOTE: \"Aboard a Flying Saucer\" is not identifiable in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Bufiles. It is to be noted that correspondent did not",
